eep住進步啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece19fa7ed66771152d62cc47c37db217240accc","tid":1957621,"uid":228487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711b71588f4609dab371b4c5cd7fb5b0db494261","tid":1957621,"uid":304397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f2ba2acf4f326a7366fd44411ebdee0622e29857","tid":1957621,"uid":228487,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T08:43:03.000Z","msg":"前幾日諗住上網學下d基本功先<br />\n但愈畫愈悶，同埋愈畫愈lose<br />\n冇人教又唔點開頭好<br />\n<br />\n之後尋日見到d留言<br />\n我決定聽大家講9畫同畫d自己鐘意既野<br />\n雖然都係畫得好核突<br />\n但開始feel到畫畫個種開心同滿足感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝大家，希望可以keep住畫同keep住進步啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1511c885f13d78db4f76cdb2b81232d6b8b8937e","tid":1957621,"uid":304397,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T09:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6fac3c8172a560a0e9177718b46922a8636f0f","tid":1957621,"uid":353647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"連登有個巴打好好，開咗好多po教畫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>小眾期待嘅畫畫教學即將出爐-頭骨篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1933897\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1933897</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你講我畫：動作姿勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1871066\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1871066</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[頭部人體學] 我應該點學畫頭像啊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672667\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672667</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好